    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Slender parts of objects, such as the vertical support of a vessel which unites its bowl to its base or the tubelike portion of a pipe that fits snugly into the bowl.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
